${color 00FF00}${font :size=8}DOWN ${downspeedf enp42s0}${goto 100}${downspeedgraph enp42s0 12,180 000000 00FF00}${goto 300}${color FF0000}UP ${upspeedf enp42s0}${goto 400}${upspeedgraph enp42s0 12,180 000000 FF0000}
